  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figure or AMSTERDAM - Chart 10-2 from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017.<br>You are approaching AMSTERDAM via REKKEN 2A. Which of the following procedures should be followed in case of a radio communication failure?</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<div>Follow the procedures provided on the 10-1P pages of your route manual.</div>",
    "b": "<div>Fly a holding pattern for at least 7 minutes.</div>",
    "c": "<div>Continue on a direct course towards the airport.</div>",
    "d": "<div>Descend below the ceiling and continue VFR to the airport.</div>"
  },
  "correctOption": "a",
